    dc:description "Figure 11. Puparium of Zaprionus neglectus Collart, 1937 a, Zaprionus inermis Collart, 1937 b, Zaprionus cercus Chassagnard & McEvey, 1992 c, Zaprionus santomensis Yassin & David, sp. n. d, Zaprionus lachaisei Yassin & David, sp. n. e and Zaprionus vittiger Coquillett, 1902 f.", "Figure 13. Male genitalia and spermatheca of Zaprionus lachaisei Yassin & David, sp. n. a, b, and Zaprionus santomensis Yassin & David, sp. n. c, d.", "Figure 5. Tarsomeres of male foreleg of Zaprionus neglectus Collart, 1937 a, Zaprionus kololdkinae Chassagnard & Tsacas, 1987 b, Zaprionus lachaisei Yassin & David, sp. n. c, Zaprionus taronus Chassagnard & Tsacas, 1993 d, and Zaprionus santomensis Yassin & David, sp. n. e." ;
